{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HtUBZ5JfePC56maaiTVZct","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→:root {\n     2→    --bg: #fff;\n     3→    --bg-surface: #f8f9fa;\n     4→    --text: #1a1a1a;\n     5→    --text-muted: #6b7280;\n     6→    --border: #e5e7eb;\n     7→    --link: #2563eb;\n     8→    --font: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;\n     9→    --mono: ui-monospace, \"Cascadia Code\", \"Fira Code\", monospace;\n    10→    --radius: 4px;\n    11→\n    12→    --badge-pending-bg: #fef3c7;\n    13→    --badge-pending-text: #92400e;\n    14→    --badge-running-bg: #dbeafe;\n    15→    --badge-running-text: #1e40af;\n    16→    --badge-succeeded-bg: #d1fae5;\n    17→    --badge-succeeded-text: #065f46;\n    18→    --badge-failed-bg: #fee2e2;\n    19→    --badge-failed-text: #991b1b;\n    20→    --badge-cancelled-bg: #f3f4f6;\n    21→    --badge-cancelled-text: #4b5563;\n    22→    --badge-stopped-bg: #e5e7eb;\n    23→    --badge-stopped-text: #4b5563;\n    24→\n    25→    --error-bg: #fef2f2;\n    26→    --error-border: #fca5a5;\n    27→    --error-text: #991b1b;\n    28→}\n    29→\n    30→@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {\n    31→    :root {\n    32→        --bg: #111827;\n    33→        --bg-surface: #1f2937;\n    34→        --text: #f3f4f6;\n    35→        --text-muted: #9ca3af;\n    36→        --border: #374151;\n    37→        --link: #60a5fa;\n    38→\n    39→        --badge-pending-bg: #78350f;\n    40→        --badge-pending-text: #fde68a;\n    41→        --badge-running-bg: #1e3a5f;\n    42→        --badge-running-text: #93c5fd;\n    43→        --badge-succeeded-bg: #064e3b;\n    44→        --badge-succeeded-text: #6ee7b7;\n    45→        --badge-failed-bg: #7f1d1d;\n    46→        --badge-failed-text: #fca5a5;\n    47→        --badge-cancelled-bg: #374151;\n    48→        --badge-cancelled-text: #9ca3af;\n    49→        --badge-stopped-bg: #374151;\n    50→        --badge-stopped-text: #9ca3af;\n    51→\n    52→        --error-bg: #450a0a;\n    53→        --error-border: #7f1d1d;\n    54→        --error-text: #fca5a5;\n    55→    }\n    56→}\n    57→\n    58→*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }\n    59→\n    60→body {\n    61→    margin: 0;\n    62→    font-family: var(--font);\n    63→    background: var(--bg);\n    64→    color: var(--text);\n    65→    line-height: 1.5;\n    66→}\n    67→\n    68→.container {\n    69→    max-width: 1100px;\n    70→    margin: 0 auto;\n    71→    padding: 0 1rem;\n    72→}\n    73→\n    74→a { color: var(--link); text-decoration: none; }\n    75→a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }\n    76→\n    77→.navbar {\n    78→    background: var(--bg-surface);\n    79→    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n    80→    padding: 0.75rem 0;\n    81→    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n    82→}\n    83→\n    84→.logo {\n    85→    font-weight: 700;\n    86→    font-size: 1.1rem;\n    87→    color: var(--text);\n    88→}\n    89→.logo:hover { text-decoration: none; }\n    90→\n    91→h1 {\n    92→    font-size: 1.4rem;\n    93→    margin: 0 0 1rem;\n    94→    display: flex;\n    95→    align-items: center;\n    96→    gap: 0.5rem;\n    97→    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    98→}\n    99→\n   100→h1 a { font-weight: 400; }\n   101→\n   102→h2 {\n   103→    font-size: 1.1rem;\n   104→    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem;\n   105→}\n   106→\n   107→/* Badges */\n   108→.badge {\n   109→    display: inline-block;\n   110→    padding: 0.15em 0.55em;\n   111→    border-radius: var(--radius);\n   112→    font-size: 0.8rem;\n   113→    font-weight: 600;\n   114→    white-space: nowrap;\n   115→}\n   116→\n   117→.badge-pending  { background: var(--badge-pending-bg);  color: var(--badge-pending-text); }\n   118→.badge-running  { background: var(--badge-running-bg);  color: var(--badge-running-text); animation: pulse 2s infinite; }\n   119→.badge-succeeded { background: var(--badge-succeeded-bg); color: var(--badge-succeeded-text); }\n   120→.badge-failed   { background: var(--badge-failed-bg);   color: var(--badge-failed-text); }\n   121→.badge-cancelled { background: var(--badge-cancelled-bg); color: var(--badge-cancelled-text); }\n   122→.badge-stopped  { background: var(--badge-stopped-bg);  color: var(--badge-stopped-text); }\n   123→\n   124→@keyframes pulse {\n   125→    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }\n   126→    50% { opacity: 0.6; }\n   127→}\n   128→\n   129→/* Tables */\n   130→.runs-table {\n   131→    width: 100%;\n   132→    border-collapse: collapse;\n   133→    font-size: 0.9rem;\n   134→}\n   135→\n   136→.runs-table th,\n   137→.runs-table td {\n   138→    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;\n   139→    text-align: left;\n   140→    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n   141→}\n   142→\n   143→.runs-table th {\n   144→    background: var(--bg-surface);\n   145→    font-weight: 600;\n   146→    font-size: 0.8rem;\n   147→    text-transform: uppercase;\n   148→    letter-spacing: 0.03em;\n   149→    color: var(--text-muted);\n   150→}\n   151→\n   152→.runs-table tr:hover { background: var(--bg-surface); }\n   153→.detail-row:hover { background: inherit; }\n   154→.step-row { cursor: pointer; }\n   155→.output-row td { padding: 0 !important; }\n   156→.step-output {\n   157→    background: var(--bg-surface);\n   158→    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n   159→    border-radius: var(--radius);\n   160→    padding: 0.75rem;\n   161→    font-family: var(--mono);\n   162→    font-size: 0.8rem;\n   163→    max-height: 500px;\n   164→    overflow: auto;\n   165→    white-space: pre-wrap;\n   166→    word-break: break-word;\n   167→    margin: 0.25rem 0.75rem 0.75rem;\n   168→}\n   169→\n   170→.mono { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.85em; }\n   171→.empty { color: var(--text-muted); text-align: center; padding: 2rem 0; }\n   172→.error-cell { color: var(--badge-failed-text); font-size: 0.85em; }\n   173→\n   174→/* Run metadata */\n   175→.run-meta dl {\n   176→    display: grid;\n   177→    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;\n   178→    gap: 0.25rem 1rem;\n   179→    margin: 0 0 1rem;\n   180→    font-size: 0.9rem;\n   181→}\n   182→\n   183→.run-meta dt { color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 600; }\n   184→.run-meta dd { margin: 0; }\n   185→\n   186→/* Error box */\n   187→.error-box {\n   188→    background: var(--error-bg);\n   189→    border: 1px solid var(--error-border);\n   190→    color: var(--error-text);\n   191→    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;\n   192→    border-radius: var(--radius);\n   193→    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n   194→    font-size: 0.9rem;\n   195→}\n   196→\n   197→/* Details / pre */\n   198→details {\n   199→    margin: 0.5rem 0;\n   200→}\n   201→\n   202→details summary {\n   203→    cursor: pointer;\n   204→    font-weight: 600;\n   205→    font-size: 0.85rem;\n   206→    color: var(--text-muted);\n   207→}\n   208→\n   209→details pre {\n   210→    background: var(--bg-surface);\n   211→    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n   212→    border-radius: var(--radius);\n   213→    padding: 0.75rem;\n   214→    font-family: var(--mono);\n   215→    font-size: 0.8rem;\n   216→    max-height: 400px;\n   217→    overflow: auto;\n   218→    white-space: pre-wrap;\n   219→    word-break: break-word;\n   220→    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;\n   221→}\n   222→\n   223→/* Project filter */\n   224→.project-filter {\n   225→    display: flex;\n   226→    align-items: center;\n   227→    gap: 0.5rem;\n   228→    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n   229→    font-size: 0.9rem;\n   230→}\n   231→\n   232→.project-filter label {\n   233→    font-weight: 600;\n   234→    color: var(--text-muted);\n   235→}\n   236→\n   237→.project-filter select {\n   238→    font-family: var(--font);\n   239→    font-size: 0.9rem;\n   240→    padding: 0.3rem 0.5rem;\n   241→    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n   242→    border-radius: var(--radius);\n   243→    background: var(--bg);\n   244→    color: var(--text);\n   245→    cursor: pointer;\n   246→}\n   247→\n   248→/* Project cards */\n   249→.project-cards {\n   250→    display: grid;\n   251→    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n   252→    gap: 1rem;\n   253→}\n   254→\n   255→.project-card {\n   256→    background: var(--bg-surface);\n   257→    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n   258→    border-radius: var(--radius);\n   259→    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;\n   260→    display: flex;\n   261→    flex-direction: column;\n   262→    gap: 0.75rem;\n   263→}\n   264→\n   265→.project-header {\n   266→    display: flex;\n   267→    align-items: center;\n   268→    gap: 0.5rem;\n   269→}\n   270→\n   271→.project-name {\n   272→    font-weight: 600;\n   273→    font-size: 1.05rem;\n   274→}\n   275→\n   276→/* Health indicator dots */\n   277→.health-dot {\n   278→    display: inline-block;\n   279→    width: 12px;\n   280→    height: 12px;\n   281→    border-radius: 50%;\n   282→    flex-shrink: 0;\n   283→}\n   284→\n   285→.health-green  { background: #22c55e; }\n   286→.health-yellow { background: #eab308; }\n   287→.health-red    { background: #ef4444; }\n   288→.health-grey   { background: #9ca3af; }\n   289→.health-blue   { background: #3b82f6; animation: pulse 2s infinite; }\n   290→\n   291→/* Project stats */\n   292→.project-stats {\n   293→    display: flex;\n   294→    gap: 1.5rem;\n   295→}\n   296→\n   297→.stat {\n   298→    display: flex;\n   299→    flex-direction: column;\n   300→}\n   301→\n   302→.stat-value {\n   303→    font-weight: 700;\n   304→    font-size: 1.1rem;\n   305→}\n   306→\n   307→.stat-label {\n   308→    font-size: 0.75rem;\n   309→    color: var(--text-muted);\n   310→    text-transform: uppercase;\n   311→    letter-spacing: 0.03em;\n   312→}\n   313→\n   314→/* Mini run history dots */\n   315→.run-history {\n   316→    display: flex;\n   317→    gap: 4px;\n   318→    align-items: center;\n   319→    min-height: 16px;\n   320→}\n   321→\n   322→.run-dot {\n   323→    display: inline-block;\n   324→    width: 10px;\n   325→    height: 10px;\n   326→    border-radius: 50%;\n   327→}\n   328→\n   329→.run-dot-succeeded { background: #22c55e; }\n   330→.run-dot-failed    { background: #ef4444; }\n   331→.run-dot-cancelled { background: #9ca3af; }\n   332→.run-dot-running   { background: #3b82f6; animation: pulse 2s infinite; }\n   333→.run-dot-pending   { background: #eab308; }\n   334→\n   335→/* Action buttons */\n   336→.project-actions {\n   337→    display: flex;\n   338→    gap: 0.5rem;\n   339→    margin-top: 0.25rem;\n   340→}\n   341→\n   342→.btn {\n   343→    display: inline-block;\n   344→    padding: 0.35em 0.75em;\n   345→    border-radius: var(--radius);\n   346→    font-family: var(--font);\n   347→    font-size: 0.8rem;\n   348→    font-weight: 600;\n   349→    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n   350→    cursor: pointer;\n   351→    text-decoration: none;\n   352→    white-space: nowrap;\n   353→}\n   354→\n   355→.btn:hover { text-decoration: none; }\n   356→\n   357→.btn-secondary {\n   358→    background: var(--bg);\n   359→    color: var(--link);\n   360→}\n   361→\n   362→.btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--bg-surface); }\n   363→\n   364→.btn-primary {\n   365→    background: var(--link);\n   366→    color: #fff;\n   367→    border-color: var(--link);\n   368→}\n   369→\n   370→.btn-primary:hover { opacity: 0.9; }\n   371→\n   372→.btn-danger {\n   373→    background: var(--badge-failed-bg);\n   374→    color: var(--badge-failed-text);\n   375→    border-color: var(--error-border);\n   376→}\n   377→\n   378→.btn-danger:hover { opacity: 0.8; }\n   379→\n   380→.btn-sm { font-size: 0.75rem; padding: 0.15em 0.45em; }\n   381→\n   382→.btn:disabled {\n   383→    opacity: 0.6;\n   384→    cursor: not-allowed;\n   385→}\n   386→\n   387→/* Log viewer */\n   388→.log-viewer {\n   389→    background: var(--bg-surface);\n   390→    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n   391→    border-radius: var(--radius);\n   392→    max-height: 600px;\n   393→    overflow: auto;\n   394→    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n   395→}\n   396→\n   397→.log-viewer pre {\n   398→    margin: 0;\n   399→    padding: 0.75rem;\n   400→    font-family: var(--mono);\n   401→    font-size: 0.8rem;\n   402→    white-space: pre-wrap;\n   403→    word-break: break-word;\n   404→    line-height: 1.4;\n   405→}\n   406→\n   407→.log-line { display: block; }\n   408→.log-type-status { color: var(--badge-running-text); }\n   409→.log-type-llm { color: var(--badge-succeeded-text); }\n   410→.log-type-script { color: var(--text); }\n   411→\n   412→/* Panels */\n   413→.panel {\n   414→    background: var(--bg-surface);\n   415→    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n   416→    border-radius: var(--radius);\n   417→    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n   418→}\n   419→\n   420→.panel-header {\n   421→    font-weight: 700;\n   422→    font-size: 0.9rem;\n   423→    padding: 0.6rem 1rem;\n   424→    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n   425→    text-transform: uppercase;\n   426→    letter-spacing: 0.03em;\n   427→    color: var(--text-muted);\n   428→}\n   429→\n   430→.panel-body {\n   431→    padding: 1rem;\n   432→}\n   433→\n   434→/* Tabs */\n   435→.tab-bar {\n   436→    display: flex;\n   437→    gap: 0;\n   438→    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n   439→    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n   440→}\n   441→.tab-bar:empty {\n   442→    display: none;\n   443→}\n   444→\n   445→.tab-btn {\n   446→    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;\n   447→    font-family: var(--font);\n   448→    font-size: 0.85rem;\n   449→    font-weight: 600;\n   450→    background: none;\n   451→    border: none;\n   452→    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;\n   453→    color: var(--text-muted);\n   454→    cursor: pointer;\n   455→}\n   456→\n   457→.tab-btn:hover { color: var(--text); }\n   458→.tab-btn.tab-active { color: var(--link); border-bottom-color: var(--link); }\n   459→\n   460→/* DAG */\n   461→.dag-svg { display: block; margin: 0 auto; }\n   462→\n   463→.dag-node-rect {\n   464→    fill: var(--bg);\n   465→    stroke: var(--border);\n   466→    stroke-width: 1.5;\n   467→    rx: 4;\n   468→}\n   469→\n   470→.dag-node:hover .dag-node-rect { stroke: var(--link); stroke-width: 2; }\n   471→\n   472→.dag-node-text {\n   473→    font-family: var(--font);\n   474→    font-size: 13px;\n   475→    fill: var(--text);\n   476→}\n   477→\n   478→.dag-edge {\n   479→    fill: none;\n   480→    stroke: var(--text-muted);\n   481→    stroke-width: 1.5;\n   482→}\n   483→\n   484→.dag-edge-label {\n   485→    font-family: var(--font);\n   486→    font-size: 10px;\n   487→    fill: var(--text-muted);\n   488→    text-anchor: middle;\n   489→}\n   490→\n   491→.dag-terminal-done { fill: var(--badge-succeeded-bg); stroke: var(--badge-succeeded-text); }\n   492→.dag-terminal-abort { fill: var(--badge-failed-bg); stroke: var(--badge-failed-text); }\n   493→\n   494→/* Drawer */\n   495→.drawer {\n   496→    position: fixed;\n   497→    top: 0;\n   498→    right: -420px;\n   499→    width: 400px;\n   500→    height: 100vh;\n   501→    background: var(--bg-surface);\n   502→    border-left: 1px solid var(--border);\n   503→    box-shadow: -4px 0 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n   504→    transition: right 0.25s ease;\n   505→    z-index: 100;\n   506→    display: flex;\n   507→    flex-direction: column;\n   508→    overflow: hidden;\n   509→}\n   510→\n   511→.drawer.drawer-open { right: 0; }\n   512→\n   513→.drawer-header {\n   514→    display: flex;\n   515→    justify-content: space-between;\n   516→    align-items: center;\n   517→    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;\n   518→    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n   519→    font-weight: 700;\n   520→    font-size: 1rem;\n   521→}\n   522→\n   523→.drawer-close {\n   524→    background: none;\n   525→    border: none;\n   526→    font-size: 1.4rem;\n   527→    cursor: pointer;\n   528→    color: var(--text-muted);\n   529→    padding: 0 0.25rem;\n   530→}\n   531→\n   532→.drawer-close:hover { color: var(--text); }\n   533→\n   534→.drawer-body {\n   535→    padding: 1rem;\n   536→    overflow-y: auto;\n   537→    flex: 1;\n   538→}\n   539→\n   540→.drawer-body pre {\n   541→    background: var(--bg);\n   542→    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n   543→    border-radius: var(--radius);\n   544→    padding: 0.75rem;\n   545→    font-family: var(--mono);\n   546→    font-size: 0.8rem;\n   547→    max-height: 400px;\n   548→    overflow: auto;\n   549→    white-space: pre-wrap;\n   550→    word-break: break-word;\n   551→}\n   552→\n   553→/* Diff block */\n   554→.diff-block {\n   555→    background: var(--bg);\n   556→    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n   557→    border-radius: var(--radius);\n   558→    padding: 0.5rem;\n   559→    font-family: var(--mono);\n   560→    font-size: 0.75rem;\n   561→    max-height: 300px;\n   562→    overflow: auto;\n   563→    white-space: pre-wrap;\n   564→    word-break: break-word;\n   565→    margin: 0.25rem 0 0.5rem;\n   566→}\n   567→\n   568→/* Orchestrator status */\n   569→.orch-status { font-size: 0.9rem; }\n   570→\n   571→/* Run tree grouping */\n   572→.run-parent-row { opacity: 0.7; }\n   573→.run-parent-row td:first-child { font-weight: 600; }\n   574→.run-child-row td:first-child { padding-left: 2rem; }\n   575→.run-child-row td:first-child::before {\n   576→    content: \"\\2514\\00a0\";\n   577→    color: var(--text-muted);\n   578→}\n   579→.tree-toggle {\n   580→    cursor: pointer;\n   581→    background: none;\n   582→    border: none;\n   583→    font-size: 0.75rem;\n   584→    color: var(--text-muted);\n   585→    padding: 0 0.25rem;\n   586→    margin-right: 0.25rem;\n   587→}\n   588→.tree-toggle:hover { color: var(--text); }\n   589→.parent-run-link { font-weight: 400; color: var(--text-muted); }\n   590→.parent-run-link:hover { color: var(--link); }\n   591→\n   592→/* Responsive */\n   593→@media (max-width: 768px) {\n   594→    .runs-table { font-size: 0.8rem; }\n   595→    .runs-table th, .runs-table td { padding: 0.4rem 0.5rem; }\n   596→    .run-meta dl { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n   597→    .project-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n   598→    .log-viewer { max-height: 400px; }\n   599→    .drawer { width: 100%; right: -100%; }\n   600→}\n   601→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4c63b3e9-21a0-4a0c-87f3-97db17cd05ef","uuid":"4e613829-1e67-4a17-9a00-dcdf0fcc4447","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/internal/adapters/web/static/style.css","content":":root {\n    --bg: #fff;\n    --bg-surface: #f8f9fa;\n    --text: #1a1a1a;\n    --text-muted: #6b7280;\n    --border: #e5e7eb;\n    --link: #2563eb;\n    --font: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;\n    --mono: ui-monospace, \"Cascadia Code\", \"Fira Code\", monospace;\n    --radius: 4px;\n\n    --badge-pending-bg: #fef3c7;\n    --badge-pending-text: #92400e;\n    --badge-running-bg: #dbeafe;\n    --badge-running-text: #1e40af;\n    --badge-succeeded-bg: #d1fae5;\n    --badge-succeeded-text: #065f46;\n    --badge-failed-bg: #fee2e2;\n    --badge-failed-text: #991b1b;\n    --badge-cancelled-bg: #f3f4f6;\n    --badge-cancelled-text: #4b5563;\n    --badge-stopped-bg: #e5e7eb;\n    --badge-stopped-text: #4b5563;\n\n    --error-bg: #fef2f2;\n    --error-border: #fca5a5;\n    --error-text: #991b1b;\n}\n\n@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {\n    :root {\n        --bg: #111827;\n        --bg-surface: #1f2937;\n        --text: #f3f4f6;\n        --text-muted: #9ca3af;\n        --border: #374151;\n        --link: #60a5fa;\n\n        --badge-pending-bg: #78350f;\n        --badge-pending-text: #fde68a;\n        --badge-running-bg: #1e3a5f;\n        --badge-running-text: #93c5fd;\n        --badge-succeeded-bg: #064e3b;\n        --badge-succeeded-text: #6ee7b7;\n        --badge-failed-bg: #7f1d1d;\n        --badge-failed-text: #fca5a5;\n        --badge-cancelled-bg: #374151;\n        --badge-cancelled-text: #9ca3af;\n        --badge-stopped-bg: #374151;\n        --badge-stopped-text: #9ca3af;\n\n        --error-bg: #450a0a;\n        --error-border: #7f1d1d;\n        --error-text: #fca5a5;\n    }\n}\n\n*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }\n\nbody {\n    margin: 0;\n    font-family: var(--font);\n    background: var(--bg);\n    color: var(--text);\n    line-height: 1.5;\n}\n\n.container {\n    max-width: 1100px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    padding: 0 1rem;\n}\n\na { color: var(--link); text-decoration: none; }\na:hover { text-decoration: underline; }\n\n.navbar {\n    background: var(--bg-surface);\n    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n    padding: 0.75rem 0;\n    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n}\n\n.logo {\n    font-weight: 700;\n    font-size: 1.1rem;\n    color: var(--text);\n}\n.logo:hover { text-decoration: none; }\n\nh1 {\n    font-size: 1.4rem;\n    margin: 0 0 1rem;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 0.5rem;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n}\n\nh1 a { font-weight: 400; }\n\nh2 {\n    font-size: 1.1rem;\n    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem;\n}\n\n/* Badges */\n.badge {\n    display: inline-block;\n    padding: 0.15em 0.55em;\n    border-radius: var(--radius);\n    font-size: 0.8rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n}\n\n.badge-pending  { background: var(--badge-pending-bg);  color: var(--badge-pending-text); }\n.badge-running  { background: var(--badge-running-bg);  color: var(--badge-running-text); animation: pulse 2s infinite; }\n.badge-succeeded { background: var(--badge-succeeded-bg); color: var(--badge-succeeded-text); }\n.badge-failed   { background: var(--badge-failed-bg);   color: var(--badge-failed-text); }\n.badge-cancelled { background: var(--badge-cancelled-bg); color: var(--badge-cancelled-text); }\n.badge-stopped  { background: var(--badge-stopped-bg);  color: var(--badge-stopped-text); }\n\n@keyframes pulse {\n    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }\n    50% { opacity: 0.6; }\n}\n\n/* Tables */\n.runs-table {\n    width: 100%;\n    border-collapse: collapse;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n}\n\n.runs-table th,\n.runs-table td {\n    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;\n    text-align: left;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n}\n\n.runs-table th {\n    background: var(--bg-surface);\n    font-weight: 600;\n    font-size: 0.8rem;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 0.03em;\n    color: var(--text-muted);\n}\n\n.runs-table tr:hover { background: var(--bg-surface); }\n.detail-row:hover { background: inherit; }\n.step-row { cursor: pointer; }\n.output-row td { padding: 0 !important; }\n.step-output {\n    background: var(--bg-surface);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n    border-radius: var(--radius);\n    padding: 0.75rem;\n    font-family: var(--mono);\n    font-size: 0.8rem;\n    max-height: 500px;\n    overflow: auto;\n    white-space: pre-wrap;\n    word-break: break-word;\n    margin: 0.25rem 0.75rem 0.75rem;\n}\n\n.mono { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.85em; }\n.empty { color: var(--text-muted); text-align: center; padding: 2rem 0; }\n.error-cell { color: var(--badge-failed-text); font-size: 0.85em; }\n\n/* Run metadata */\n.run-meta dl {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;\n    gap: 0.25rem 1rem;\n    margin: 0 0 1rem;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n}\n\n.run-meta dt { color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 600; }\n.run-meta dd { margin: 0; }\n\n/* Error box */\n.error-box {\n    background: var(--error-bg);\n    border: 1px solid var(--error-border);\n    color: var(--error-text);\n    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;\n    border-radius: var(--radius);\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n}\n\n/* Details / pre */\ndetails {\n    margin: 0.5rem 0;\n}\n\ndetails summary {\n    cursor: pointer;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    font-size: 0.85rem;\n    color: var(--text-muted);\n}\n\ndetails pre {\n    background: var(--bg-surface);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n    border-radius: var(--radius);\n    padding: 0.75rem;\n    font-family: var(--mono);\n    font-size: 0.8rem;\n    max-height: 400px;\n    overflow: auto;\n    white-space: pre-wrap;\n    word-break: break-word;\n    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;\n}\n\n/* Project filter */\n.project-filter {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 0.5rem;\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n}\n\n.project-filter label {\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: var(--text-muted);\n}\n\n.project-filter select {\n    font-family: var(--font);\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n    padding: 0.3rem 0.5rem;\n    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n    border-radius: var(--radius);\n    background: var(--bg);\n    color: var(--text);\n    cursor: pointer;\n}\n\n/* Project cards */\n.project-cards {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n    gap: 1rem;\n}\n\n.project-card {\n    background: var(--bg-surface);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n    border-radius: var(--radius);\n    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 0.75rem;\n}\n\n.project-header {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 0.5rem;\n}\n\n.project-name {\n    font-weight: 600;\n    font-size: 1.05rem;\n}\n\n/* Health indicator dots */\n.health-dot {\n    display: inline-block;\n    width: 12px;\n    height: 12px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n}\n\n.health-green  { background: #22c55e; }\n.health-yellow { background: #eab308; }\n.health-red    { background: #ef4444; }\n.health-grey   { background: #9ca3af; }\n.health-blue   { background: #3b82f6; animation: pulse 2s infinite; }\n\n/* Project stats */\n.project-stats {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 1.5rem;\n}\n\n.stat {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n}\n\n.stat-value {\n    font-weight: 700;\n    font-size: 1.1rem;\n}\n\n.stat-label {\n    font-size: 0.75rem;\n    color: var(--text-muted);\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 0.03em;\n}\n\n/* Mini run history dots */\n.run-history {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 4px;\n    align-items: center;\n    min-height: 16px;\n}\n\n.run-dot {\n    display: inline-block;\n    width: 10px;\n    height: 10px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n}\n\n.run-dot-succeeded { background: #22c55e; }\n.run-dot-failed    { background: #ef4444; }\n.run-dot-cancelled { background: #9ca3af; }\n.run-dot-running   { background: #3b82f6; animation: pulse 2s infinite; }\n.run-dot-pending   { background: #eab308; }\n\n/* Action buttons */\n.project-actions {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 0.5rem;\n    margin-top: 0.25rem;\n}\n\n.btn {\n    display: inline-block;\n    padding: 0.35em 0.75em;\n    border-radius: var(--radius);\n    font-family: var(--font);\n    font-size: 0.8rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n    cursor: pointer;\n    text-decoration: none;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n}\n\n.btn:hover { text-decoration: none; }\n\n.btn-secondary {\n    background: var(--bg);\n    color: var(--link);\n}\n\n.btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--bg-surface); }\n\n.btn-primary {\n    background: var(--link);\n    color: #fff;\n    border-color: var(--link);\n}\n\n.btn-primary:hover { opacity: 0.9; }\n\n.btn-danger {\n    background: var(--badge-failed-bg);\n    color: var(--badge-failed-text);\n    border-color: var(--error-border);\n}\n\n.btn-danger:hover { opacity: 0.8; }\n\n.btn-sm { font-size: 0.75rem; padding: 0.15em 0.45em; }\n\n.btn:disabled {\n    opacity: 0.6;\n    cursor: not-allowed;\n}\n\n/* Log viewer */\n.log-viewer {\n    background: var(--bg-surface);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n    border-radius: var(--radius);\n    max-height: 600px;\n    overflow: auto;\n    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n}\n\n.log-viewer pre {\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 0.75rem;\n    font-family: var(--mono);\n    font-size: 0.8rem;\n    white-space: pre-wrap;\n    word-break: break-word;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n}\n\n.log-line { display: block; }\n.log-type-status { color: var(--badge-running-text); }\n.log-type-llm { color: var(--badge-succeeded-text); }\n.log-type-script { color: var(--text); }\n\n/* Panels */\n.panel {\n    background: var(--bg-surface);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n    border-radius: var(--radius);\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n}\n\n.panel-header {\n    font-weight: 700;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n    padding: 0.6rem 1rem;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 0.03em;\n    color: var(--text-muted);\n}\n\n.panel-body {\n    padding: 1rem;\n}\n\n/* Tabs */\n.tab-bar {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 0;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n}\n.tab-bar:empty {\n    display: none;\n}\n\n.tab-btn {\n    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;\n    font-family: var(--font);\n    font-size: 0.85rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    background: none;\n    border: none;\n    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;\n    color: var(--text-muted);\n    cursor: pointer;\n}\n\n.tab-btn:hover { color: var(--text); }\n.tab-btn.tab-active { color: var(--link); border-bottom-color: var(--link); }\n\n/* DAG */\n.dag-svg { display: block; margin: 0 auto; }\n\n.dag-node-rect {\n    fill: var(--bg);\n    stroke: var(--border);\n    stroke-width: 1.5;\n    rx: 4;\n}\n\n.dag-node:hover .dag-node-rect { stroke: var(--link); stroke-width: 2; }\n\n.dag-node-text {\n    font-family: var(--font);\n    font-size: 13px;\n    fill: var(--text);\n}\n\n.dag-edge {\n    fill: none;\n    stroke: var(--text-muted);\n    stroke-width: 1.5;\n}\n\n.dag-edge-label {\n    font-family: var(--font);\n    font-size: 10px;\n    fill: var(--text-muted);\n    text-anchor: middle;\n}\n\n.dag-terminal-done { fill: var(--badge-succeeded-bg); stroke: var(--badge-succeeded-text); }\n.dag-terminal-abort { fill: var(--badge-failed-bg); stroke: var(--badge-failed-text); }\n\n/* Drawer */\n.drawer {\n    position: fixed;\n    top: 0;\n    right: -420px;\n    width: 400px;\n    height: 100vh;\n    background: var(--bg-surface);\n    border-left: 1px solid var(--border);\n    box-shadow: -4px 0 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n    transition: right 0.25s ease;\n    z-index: 100;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.drawer.drawer-open { right: 0; }\n\n.drawer-header {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n    font-weight: 700;\n    font-size: 1rem;\n}\n\n.drawer-close {\n    background: none;\n    border: none;\n    font-size: 1.4rem;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    color: var(--text-muted);\n    padding: 0 0.25rem;\n}\n\n.drawer-close:hover { color: var(--text); }\n\n.drawer-body {\n    padding: 1rem;\n    overflow-y: auto;\n    flex: 1;\n}\n\n.drawer-body pre {\n    background: var(--bg);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n    border-radius: var(--radius);\n    padding: 0.75rem;\n    font-family: var(--mono);\n    font-size: 0.8rem;\n    max-height: 400px;\n    overflow: auto;\n    white-space: pre-wrap;\n    word-break: break-word;\n}\n\n/* Diff block */\n.diff-block {\n    background: var(--bg);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n    border-radius: var(--radius);\n    padding: 0.5rem;\n    font-family: var(--mono);\n    font-size: 0.75rem;\n    max-height: 300px;\n    overflow: auto;\n    white-space: pre-wrap;\n    word-break: break-word;\n    margin: 0.25rem 0 0.5rem;\n}\n\n/* Orchestrator status */\n.orch-status { font-size: 0.9rem; }\n\n/* Run tree grouping */\n.run-parent-row { opacity: 0.7; }\n.run-parent-row td:first-child { font-weight: 600; }\n.run-child-row td:first-child { padding-left: 2rem; }\n.run-child-row td:first-child::before {\n    content: \"\\2514\\00a0\";\n    color: var(--text-muted);\n}\n.tree-toggle {\n    cursor: pointer;\n    background: none;\n    border: none;\n    font-size: 0.75rem;\n    color: var(--text-muted);\n    padding: 0 0.25rem;\n    margin-right: 0.25rem;\n}\n.tree-toggle:hover { color: var(--text); }\n.parent-run-link { font-weight: 400; color: var(--text-muted); }\n.parent-run-link:hover { color: var(--link); }\n\n/* Responsive */\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .runs-table { font-size: 0.8rem; }\n    .runs-table th, .runs-table td { padding: 0.4rem 0.5rem; }\n    .run-meta dl { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n    .project-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n    .log-viewer { max-height: 400px; }\n    .drawer { width: 100%; right: -100%; }\n}\n","numLines":601,"startLine":1,"totalLines":601}}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_013cqrosMNaoJ1U1Dk3Fq2uM","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the current implementation. The current layout is a simple single-column vertical layout where all nodes are stacked vertically at the same X position. Wires go from the right side of one node to the left side of the next, all overlapping since everything is in one column.\n\nI need to implement a proper layout engine that:\n1. Assigns nodes to layers/columns (left-to-right flow) based on their depth in the DAG\n2. Minimizes edge crossings within layers\n3. Merges wires to common terminal nodes (done/abort) to reduce clutter\n4. Uses proper spacing for clarity\n\nLet me design the layout algorithm:\n\n\nI'll use a Sugiyama-style layered graph approach where I assign each node to a layer based on its longest path from the entry point, then order nodes within each layer to minimize edge crossings, calculate their X/Y coordinates with layers flowing left to right, and route edges between layers while merging paths that converge at terminal nodes. Writing the layout engine...\n\nFor terminal merging, I'll use a bus pattern where multiple edges converge at a single merge point before reaching the terminal—each source draws a line to that convergence point, then a single line continues to the terminal, keeping edge labels on the individual segments for clarity. I'm settling on the bus pattern from circuit diagrams—sources connect with Bezier curves to a vertical collector line, which then routes horizontally to the terminal. Now I'm writing the code to implement this layout and rendering logic. Building the layer assignment logic... Still writing layout algorithm... Sorting the layer by barycenter values, but I realize I'm trying to set properties on strings which won't work—I need to use a map to track the barycenter for each node instead.\n\nNow I'm building out the workflow visualization function, starting with a step map to look up steps by name, then collecting terminal nodes like 'done' and 'abort', and constructing both forward and reverse adjacency lists from the wires.\n\nImplementing layer assignment logic... Building the layer structure... Still writing the layout algorithm... Writing SVG markup... Writing SVG paths... Writing SVG edge paths... Writing SVG edge paths... Writing the node rendering... Finishing the SVG rendering for terminal nodes...\n\nI'm realizing there's an issue with how I'm calculating layer positions—I've been pulling from parents, but for a longest path algorithm I need to push from the entry point instead. Let me switch to a BFS approach that tracks the maximum depth as I traverse forward.\n\nI'll start with a proper topological sort using in-degree counting, then process nodes in order to assign each one to the deepest layer reachable from the entry point.\n\nContinuing with layer assignment...\n\nI need to handle the special case where entry_step is defined—it should always sit at layer 0. I'm also thinking about edges that skip layers, like when entry connects directly to a step that's several layers down. Rather than inserting dummy nodes to fill the gaps, I'll let the Bezier curves naturally span across multiple layers.\n\nNow I'm reconsidering how to handle terminals with multiple incoming edges. The cleanest approach visually would be to have each source draw a short stub that converges into a vertical collector line positioned between the sources and the terminal, then a single line from the collector reaches the terminal. I need to position this collector line at a fixed distance before the terminal (maybe 50 pixels), then route each source's Bezier curve to meet it at the appropriate height before the final connection to the terminal itself. I need to handle the case where the terminal Y falls outside the source Y range by extending the vertical collector line to encompass all points, then drawing a horizontal segment from that line to the terminal. Let me settle on drawing beziers from each source to the merge point at mergeX, a vertical line spanning from the minimum to maximum of all Y coordinates including the terminal, and finally a horizontal line connecting the merge point to the terminal.\n\nBut I'm realizing that when sources come from different layers, the merge point becomes visually awkward since edges arrive at different horizontal positions. Maybe I should just simplify this with curves instead.\n\nFor terminals with multiple incoming edges, I'll use a merge pattern where each source connects via a curve to a fixed merge point, with edge labels on those curves, then a single vertical line collects them and connects to the terminal. The merge point stays at a consistent distance before the terminal, so each curve is just a bezier from the source's right edge to that merge position.\n\nNow I need to handle the SVG viewBox properly...\n\nActually, I'll stick with the existing width/height approach but expand the SVG canvas to fit the horizontal layout. For edge cases like linear workflows, diamonds, and complex multi-terminal scenarios, the longest-path layer assignment should handle them naturally. Time to write the full implementation with proper layer assignment, barycenter ordering, clean bezier routing, and the terminal merging pattern.\n\nNow I'm looking at the actual workflow files in the project to understand what patterns I need to support, and checking the test structure to see how the layout algorithm should be validated. Since the layout engine runs entirely in JavaScript on the client side, I'll need to make sure the existing Go tests still pass while potentially adding some client-side tests for the algorithm itself.\n\nI'm going to implement the complete `showWorkflow` function with proper handling for edge cases like missing wires or empty steps. For the terminal merging logic, I'll calculate a merge point to the left of each terminal and draw bezier curves from source nodes to that merge point, then add edge labels appropriately.\n\nWriting the layout implementation... I'm using Bezier curves to smooth the connections from each source to the collector line, creating gentle horizontal curves that converge at mergeX but maintain each source's own Y position. Then the vertical collector line connects all these different Y points, with a final segment running from the collector down to the terminal node.\n\nNow I'm implementing the workflow visualization code... Now I'm implementing a topological sort using Kahn's algorithm to determine the order of steps, calculating in-degrees for each step and processing nodes with no incoming edges to build the final ordering.\n\nContinuing with the longest path calculation... Building the layer arrays and applying barycenter ordering... Finishing the sort, then moving into position calculations. I'm setting up dimensions for the nodes and layers—defining the width, height, and gaps between elements—then calculating the maximum layer height and starting to position each node within its layer based on these measurements.\n\nWriting SVG code... Drawing the normal wires now, calculating the curved paths between nodes using cubic Bezier curves and positioning the arrowheads at each connection endpoint. Writing SVG edge paths... Writing SVG paths and labels... Writing SVG nodes...\n\nNow I'm considering an edge case where nodes from earlier layers might connect directly to terminal states, bypassing intermediate steps.\n\nLet me trace through the logic: the `revAdj` map includes all wires, but terminals aren't part of the layer assignment since they're not in the `inDeg` map—only actual steps are. So the topological sort correctly ignores terminal connections when determining layers, and the merge nodes will properly handle sources from different layers converging on the same terminal. I'm realizing there's a subtle bug with how I'm handling in-degree for terminal nodes—incrementing `inDeg` for 'done' or 'abort' would create undefined entries that become NaN, but my conditional check should catch this. Let me trace through the logic more carefully to make sure the terminal node handling is actually sound throughout the barycenter ordering. Still writing topological sort...\n\nNow I'm thinking through edge cases—what happens with cycles, missing nodes, or an entry step with incoming edges. The algorithm should handle these gracefully by appending unprocessed nodes and relying on the longest-path layering to position the entry step correctly at layer 0. Before finalizing the code, I need to make sure the SVG container scrolls horizontally since the DAG could get quite wide, so I'll add overflow handling to the workflow-dag element. Writing the template replacement...","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":12444,"cache_read_input_tokens":18752,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":12444},"output_tokens":12,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4c63b3e9-21a0-4a0c-87f3-97db17cd05ef","uuid":"be1d998f-d76b-45f4-adca-1253bdbb8659"}
